{"tid":465726,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉貼420]ONEPIECE即將去到和之國了","createTime":"2017-11-11T20:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T05:45:32.000Z","uid":78533,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b7d429d08a125a3cdcefbba2a121799eae88c56b","tid":465726,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T20:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該過多兩年就會轉到和之角既故事~<br />\n<br />\n係到同大家分享下[LUFFY420]有關和之國既一D推測~<br />\n<br />\n講到和之國!今次要分享既係一直未知既角色百獸凱多<br />\n<br />\n以下就係LUFFY420既有關既推測<br />\n凱多登場<br />\n2015-08-01 Sat 12:09<br />\n和之國的推測<br />\n<a href=\"http://luffy420.blog.fc2.com/category10-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fluffy420.blog.fc2.com%2Fcategory10-1.html&d=NPHxMgBctKn2sglCROAhp5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=76c82e8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://luffy420.blog.fc2.com/category10-1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n凱多的能力推測<br />\n<a href=\"http://luffy420.blog.fc2.com/blog-entry-285.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fluffy420.blog.fc2.com%2Fblog-entry-285.html&d=NPHxMgBctKn2sglCROAhp5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=9dc2cf85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://luffy420.blog.fc2.com/blog-entry-285.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近來很少寫BLOG，也很少上討論區，大部份的想法都概括地在WEIBO發佈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com/l/u/f/luffy420/20150801120713d0f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com%2Fl%2Fu%2Ff%2Fluffy420%2F20150801120713d0f.png&h=530c4ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n百獸凱多終於正式登場，之前的推測是&quot;凱多是條吃了&lt;惡鬼果實&gt;的惡龍&quot;，現在的想法有沒變呢。其實也有點動搖的，因為如果是能力者，而凱多又真想死的話,吃兩顆果實或跳海也能如願以償。但又考慮到是否因為他是條龍的關係，這算那麼做了也不死呢，現在也不想下定論。<br />\n<br />\n這篇主要是從&quot;凱多是惡龍&quot;的觀點出發，看看能否解釋他的行為。<br />\n<br />\n凱多今回一來就出現在空島上，身邊沒有交通工具就他一人，即是他是憑自己的力量上空島的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com/l/u/f/luffy420/20150801123220ff0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com%2Fl%2Fu%2Ff%2Fluffy420%2F20150801123220ff0.png&h=4aca7e04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一個人又怎能做到呢，除了果實能力外，很大可能就是他有飛翔的能力。&quot;凱多是惡龍&quot;的話這就解釋到了，惡龍有翅膀會飛翔，要上高空一万米的空島自然不是問題。然後是掉下來完全絲毫無損，這麼強韌的肉體也可能是因為他是條惡龍的原故。(這裡不說空島掉下來再去挖溫泉的神官了，那是搞笑XD)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com/l/u/f/luffy420/20150801123450ab9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com%2Fl%2Fu%2Ff%2Fluffy420%2F20150801123450ab9.png&h=3ec81908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://blog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com/l/u/f/luffy420/201508011234525f1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com%2Fl%2Fu%2Ff%2Fluffy420%2F201508011234525f1.png&h=5852cc42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://blog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com/l/u/f/luffy420/20150801123453c72.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com%2Fl%2Fu%2Ff%2Fluffy420%2F20150801123453c72.png&h=c670b75b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後是簡述他殺不死的情況。<br />\n這些說明中看到一個要點，就是刀槍類的武器殺不死他，說明他的身體比那些刑具都要堅硬，大概因為他是惡龍的肉體。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com/l/u/f/luffy420/20150801124411e26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com%2Fl%2Fu%2Ff%2Fluffy420%2F20150801124411e26.png&h=3b14a4d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com/l/u/f/luffy420/201508011247586c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com%2Fl%2Fu%2Ff%2Fluffy420%2F201508011247586c7.png&h=0535a503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n霍金斯指出這海域的上空有&quot;怪物&quot;的空島傳說，之後奇拉看凱多又說他是&quot;怪物&quot;，這裡可能是個暗示。同時，&quot;凱多是惡龍&quot;的話，他在這海域的空中飛行時，可能被人們看到了惡龍的身影。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尾田給了他&quot;自殺&quot;的興趣，這究竟是甚麼原因令他要&quot;自殺&quot;呢?<br />\n<br />\n是因為太強，所以覺得世界太無聊?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com/l/u/f/luffy420/2015080112575574c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com%2Fl%2Fu%2Ff%2Fluffy420%2F2015080112575574c.png&h=7b33b3cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還是因為自己犯下了某個罪，而要自殺以謝罪?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com/l/u/f/luffy420/20150801125757dd1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com%2Fl%2Fu%2Ff%2Fluffy420%2F20150801125757dd1.png&h=142d8288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個以後再研究，不過從他要&quot;自殺&quot;的方向去想，420發現了他對上和之國的原因...可能是這樣的...(這個昨天在FB也說了)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com/l/u/f/luffy420/201508011304349b0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-80-origin.fc2.com%2Fl%2Fu%2Ff%2Fluffy420%2F201508011304349b0.png&h=113aecce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;聽說和之國曾有能砍惡龍的武士&quot; <br />\n<br />\n論和之國的傳說，自然想到的是龍馬留傳下來的&quot;斬龍傳說&quot;﹐。如果&quot;凱多是惡龍&quot;的話，而他又&quot;想死而死不了&quot;的話，大概會想: &quot;不妨找武士來殺我試試&quot;。這會不會就是凱多找上了和之國的原因呢。<br />\n<br />\n而點名桃之助，現在的推測都指向他是將軍的後繼人﹐而凱多可能是認為和之國最強的人是將軍吧，如果找不到將軍就找下一代將軍......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n   ---------------------------------------------------完-----------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係另人期待~<br />\n究竟佢點上空島??點解係罪人??身上既紋身係龍紋身?<br />\n有心睇OP有時都幾有趣~ <br />\n就好似N年前路飛同艾斯結拜做兄第果時漫畫角落頭有隱藏既第三個酒杯既杯邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一發現果下真係令人期待又興奮,到最後真係彈左個SABO出泥,真係好驚喜~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0af7ca0a7e532ef5a0624690526f456e9fda2a5","tid":465726,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T20:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢指既惡鬼果實係估人人果實既幻獸種"},{"pid":"61579f4de7d6bd922bcc94143513fd9a9fc952c9","tid":465726,"uid":157522